#COVID19 #vaccine walk-in alert!

Calling Rexall (345 Bloor St. East, Toronto) this morning, I was told their waitlist system had issues and "WE'RE DOING WALK-IN VACCINES ALL DAY". Zoomed over on my bike like PWH!

Wait→consent form→wait→shot→15m safety wait. <45m total. https://t.co/rjH03jnpsQ
